Description: Accelerated data analysis so you can focus on interpretation
    during data exploration instead of figuring out how to code the answers
    to your questions. This bundle evolved from the maintainer's own need
    to automate and share common analyses and visualisations. Most
    functions expect 'phyloseq' or similar data structures. Many functions
    are wrappers around, or drop-in replacements of, existing functions or
    packages; some are original creations while others are adapted from
    community sources (credits are given where appropriate). The primary
    context is microbiome, resistome, metagenomics, and eDNA research, but
    the functions are not strictly limited to those domains. Please read
    the disclaimer and double-check that functions are fit for your
    purpose; outcomes could be erroneous.
